snippet.textDisplay:
This is soooo RICH, there is layers upon layers of brilliance here... A treat after treat for the senses... and still the message so poignant yet irreverent. I love it. ABSOLUTELY LOVE the combination, the choices and then EVERYONE's devotion to excellence. Mazaa Aagayaa, Kamaal Jayi indeed! 

Not to mention how UBER excited I get anytime Shazia Manzoor's name is mentioned in my vicinity. To see her again in this avatar in all her resplendent GLORY.. and to pair her up with Hasan Raheem, one of my favorite current artists.. I feel like this track is a GIFT tailor-made JUST FOR ME. Thank You for this absolute Gem, that I will cherish for many years to come.
